<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Parcel Created - SendIt</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .parcel-info {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .tracking-number {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>ðŸ“¦ Parcel Created Successfully!</h1>
        <p>Your delivery is being processed</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{recipientName}},</h2>
        
        <p>A new parcel has been created for you and is ready for pickup.</p>
        
        <div class="tracking-number">
            Tracking Number: {{trackingNumber}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="parcel-info">
            <h3>ðŸ“‹ Parcel Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Recipient:</strong> {{recipientName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Pickup Address:</strong> {{pickupAddress}}</p>
            <p><strong>Delivery Address:</strong> {{deliveryAddress}}</p>
            {{#if weight}}<p><strong>Weight:</strong> {{weight}}</p>{{/if}}
            {{#if description}}<p><strong>Description:</strong> {{description}}</p>{{/if}}
            <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color: #667eea; font-weight: bold;">{{status}}</span></p>
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>What happens next?</strong></p>
        <ol>
            <li>Our driver will be assigned to your parcel</li>
            <li>You'll receive pickup confirmation</li>
            <li>Real-time tracking will be available</li>
            <li>Delivery updates will be sent to your email</li>
        </ol>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" class="button">Track Your Parcel</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>You can track your parcel anytime using the tracking number above.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The SendIt Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© 2025 SendIt. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This email was sent to {{recipientEmail}}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 